{"type":"message","id":"f7fc2812","parentId":"4dcb0ecf","timestamp":"2026-03-24T03:49:39.474Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_o06tugawx0kt_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 5485\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=3437\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] experiments/tic/tic_classifier.py\r\n[mutation proposed] experiments/tic/tic_classifier.py\r\n[master e2c4354] pulse: 2026-03-23 234907\n 7 files changed, 386 insertions(+), 117 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-23 234907.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-23 234907.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-23 233909.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-23 234907 - The TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) experiment is the next critical step to unify Phase 1 and Phase 2. I need to implement a classifier that identifies invariants across pulse logs and uses them to predict subsequent pulse content.\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"tide-claw","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 5485\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=3437\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] experiments/tic/tic_classifier.py\r\n[mutation proposed] experiments/tic/tic_classifier.py\r\n[master e2c4354] pulse: 2026-03-23 234907\n 7 files changed, 386 insertions(+), 117 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-23 234907.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-23 234907.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-23 233909.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-23 234907 - The TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) experiment is the next critical step to unify Phase 1 and Phase 2. I need to implement a classifier that identifies invariants across pulse logs and uses them to predict subsequent pulse content.\r\n","name":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\pulse